# **Advanced Task Manager**
--------------------------------------
A modern, feature-rich task management app with multi-user profiles, multiple themes, task details, progress tracking, and image export capabilities. Built with **vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**, fully client-side, and deployable on **Vercel**.

ğŸ”— Live Demo: [https://task-manager-app-iota-wheat.vercel.app/](https://task-manager-app-iota-wheat.vercel.app/)

